---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="What Scratch Research Co. is and why it exists.">
  <div class="about-page">

    <div class="container content-width">
      <header class="about-header">
        <p class="page-kicker">About</p>
        <h1 class="page-title">What This Is</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="about-body prose">
        <p>
          Scratch Research Co. started with a notebook and a Sunday afternoon at Augusta National.
          No phone. No leaderboard. Just the sound of the gallery, the smell of pine, and
          a growing list of things nobody mentions on TV.
        </p>

        <p>
          The goal is simple: write about golf the way you'd talk about it with someone
          who actually played and watched and wondered. Not press releases. Not scorecards.
          <em>Observations.</em>
        </p>

        <h2>How It Works</h2>

        <p>
          Every Sunday evening, once tournaments wrap globally, an automated pipeline fetches
          results, statistics, and historical context — then hands it to Claude (Anthropic's AI)
          to draft the week's issue. That draft comes to me for a read-through before it publishes.
        </p>

        <p>
          Think of it as AI-assisted, human-curated. The research is thorough. The voice stays
          consistent. And nothing publishes without a human eye on it first.
        </p>

        <h2>The Picks</h2>

        <p>
          Every issue closes with picks for the following week — players we like based on
          form, course history, and stats. We cross-reference those picks the following week.
          The misses stay on the board. That's the deal.
        </p>

        <h2>Coverage</h2>

        <p>
          PGA Tour. DP World Tour. LIV Golf. The Majors. If there's a professional stroke-play
          event of consequence ending on a Sunday, it's in scope.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.about-page { padding: 4rem 0 var(--spacing-xl); }

.about-header {
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  padding-bottom: 2rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}

.page-kicker {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  color: var(--color-accent);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.page-title {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
}

.about-body { padding-top: 0.5rem; }
</style>
